Package: divanchors
Title: A Quarto Extension for Theorem Div Anchor Links
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Douglas Ezra", "Morrison", email = "demorrison@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Quarto extension that adds visual URL anchor links to theorem
    and proof divs for HTML and RevealJS output, similarly to the built-in
    anchor-sections option for section headings.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
URL: https://github.com/d-morrison/div-anchors
BugReports: https://github.com/d-morrison/div-anchors/issues
